{"type": "article", "id": 4375, "title": "The Basura Project 挂灯", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-15T07:55:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233044qGP4SzKwjnsACbfY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t吊灯、台灯、壁灯、落地灯……也许你为家里购置了各种类型的灯饰，但仍发现有一些边边角角的地方总是无法得到灯光的眷顾。日前，来自英国的艺术设计工作室 Marc Trotereau 就针对这一问题特别设计了一款名为「The Basura Project」的不规则挂灯，选用了波浪塑胶材质制作整体框架，且具有防静电功能。The Basura Project 并没有一个固定的造型，设计团队以拼接组合的形式将多个方形模块架构组成不同形状的灯饰，以适应墙角等位置的使用。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233042XuVmO7A3tMWzFoJe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233042IL1oKpbmDsG4vZEB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66410256\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233043JAXOu3y0KPUpYhta.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66353678\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233043ERMcqnsYFk50yabu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}